OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear
OL,6,Fperiods this evening but cloudier
OL,7,Fconditions will tend to spread in from
OL,8,Fthe west overnight, perhaps giving the
OL,9,Fodd spot of light rain. Generally
OL,10,Flight winds. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSome bright spells during
OL,13,Fthe morning. However, cloud thickening
OL,14,Ffrom the west in the afternoon,
OL,15,Fbringing some outbreaks of rain for
OL,16,Fnorthern counties, remaining mostly
OL,17,Fdry elsewhere. Mild, becoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
