OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,6,Fsome rain or showers, also some
OL,7,Fbrighter spells. Strong winds likely.
OL,8,FSaturday, mostly dry, some bright
OL,9,Fspells, lighter winds. Sunday,
OL,10,Fcloudier and rather windy but likely
OL,11,Fmostly dry. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
